===string formating===
python supports multiple ways of formatting strings,incuding old style % formattig,str.formate(),and f-strings(formatited string literals).
===Escape sequences===
special character combinations that are used to represent characters that are otherwise difficult or imposiible to include directly in a string.
print("hello\\s world")
print("hello\\ns world")----new line
